1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,900
 Writer, who is the baby in your belly?

2
00:00:02,900 --> 00:00:07,800
 Yes, I think it must be Mr. Long.

3
00:00:07,800 --> 00:00:10,300
 Has Mr. Long come here to sing lately?

4
00:00:10,300 --> 00:00:14,800
 Yes, from the day I knew I was pregnant, I didn't see him come here.

